# Task Artifacts

This directory stores outputs from agent workflow stages.

## Structure

```
workflows/
├── development-workflow.md    ← Process guide
└── artifacts/                 ← Per-task outputs
    ├── implementation-plan.md
    ├── review-report.md
    └── qa-report.md
```

## Usage

When starting a new task:
1. Clear or archive previous artifacts
2. Create fresh `implementation-plan.md` during planning
3. Create `review-report.md` after implementation
4. Create `qa-report.md` after testing

Artifacts are ephemeral — they document a single task cycle. Permanent knowledge goes into `brain/`.
